<!-- Why Omori：3カラム段差カード -->
<section class="index-advantage-section bg-white pt-6 pb-9 md:pt-28 md:pb-16" aria-label="大森不動産の強み">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10">

    <!-- ヘッダー -->
    <div class="text-center mb-14 md:mb-16" data-reveal>
      <p class="section-label mb-4">OUR ADVANTAGE</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-ink leading-tight">選ばれる理由</h2>
      <span class="mt-5 mx-auto block h-px w-10 bg-[#E8621A]" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
        工務店と一体の窓口で、購入前から総額感と工事の現実性まで一度に詰められます。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ジグザグ4行 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-16 md:gap-20">

      <!-- POINT 01：画像左・テキスト右 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-16" data-reveal>
        <div class="w-full md:w-[30%] shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/images/advantage/advantage-point-01.webp" alt="" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-hidden="true" class="w-full max-w-[260px] md:max-w-[280px] object-contain">
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <div class="advantage-point__head max-md:flex max-md:flex-wrap max-md:items-center max-md:gap-x-2.5 max-md:gap-y-1 max-md:mb-4">
            <span class="advantage-point__label inline-block bg-[#E8621A] text-white text-xs font-mono-label font-medium tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 mb-4 max-md:mb-0 max-md:px-2 shrink-0" aria-label="POINT 01"><span class="md:hidden">01</span><span class="hidden md:inline" aria-hidden="true">POINT 01</span></span>
            <h3 class="advantage-point__title font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink leading-snug mb-5 max-md:mb-0 max-md:flex-1 max-md:min-w-0">失敗物件を避けられる</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">安く見える物件でも、リフォーム費用や修繕費が高くつけば結局高い買い物になります。<br class="hidden md:block">リフォーム費用を妥協して、理想の住まいから遠ざかってしまうことも。<br>大森不動産は購入前に建物の状態を工務店目線で診断し、「買っていい物件かどうか」まで判断します。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- POINT 02：テキスト左・画像右 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10 md:gap-16" data-reveal>
        <div class="w-full md:w-[30%] shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/images/advantage/advantage-point-02.webp" alt="" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-hidden="true" class="w-full max-w-[320px] md:max-w-[360px] object-contain">
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <div class="advantage-point__head max-md:flex max-md:flex-wrap max-md:items-center max-md:gap-x-2.5 max-md:gap-y-1 max-md:mb-4">
            <span class="advantage-point__label inline-block bg-[#E8621A] text-white text-xs font-mono-label font-medium tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 mb-4 max-md:mb-0 max-md:px-2 shrink-0" aria-label="POINT 02"><span class="md:hidden">02</span><span class="hidden md:inline" aria-hidden="true">POINT 02</span></span>
            <h3 class="advantage-point__title font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink leading-snug mb-5 max-md:mb-0 max-md:flex-1 max-md:min-w-0">総額で判断できる</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">普通は、不動産・リフォーム・銀行がバラバラで、最後まで総額が見えません。<br>大森不動産なら、物件価格＋諸費用＋リフォーム費用＋将来の修繕費まで含めて判断できる為、<br class="hidden md:block">購入前に総額の見通しが立ちます。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- POINT 03：画像左・テキスト右 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-16" data-reveal>
        <div class="w-full md:w-[30%] shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/images/advantage/advantage-point-03.webp" alt="" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-hidden="true" class="w-full max-w-[260px] md:max-w-[280px] object-contain">
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <div class="advantage-point__head max-md:flex max-md:flex-wrap max-md:items-center max-md:gap-x-2.5 max-md:gap-y-1 max-md:mb-4">
            <span class="advantage-point__label inline-block bg-[#E8621A] text-white text-xs font-mono-label font-medium tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 mb-4 max-md:mb-0 max-md:px-2 shrink-0" aria-label="POINT 03"><span class="md:hidden">03</span><span class="hidden md:inline" aria-hidden="true">POINT 03</span></span>
            <h3 class="advantage-point__title font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink leading-snug mb-5 max-md:mb-0 max-md:flex-1 max-md:min-w-0">工事の現実性が分かる</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">「この壁を抜きたい」「水回りを移動したい」「賃貸用に間取りを変えたい」<br class="hidden md:block">　——普通の不動産会社では、その場で判断しにくいです。<br>大森不動産なら、できる・できない・いくらかかるを早い段階ではっきりお伝えできます。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- POINT 04：テキスト左・画像右 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10 md:gap-16" data-reveal>
        <div class="w-full md:w-[30%] shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/images/advantage/advantage-point-04.webp" alt="" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-hidden="true" class="w-full max-w-[310px] md:max-w-[340px] object-contain">
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <div class="advantage-point__head max-md:flex max-md:flex-wrap max-md:items-center max-md:gap-x-2.5 max-md:gap-y-1 max-md:mb-4">
            <span class="advantage-point__label inline-block bg-[#E8621A] text-white text-xs font-mono-label font-medium tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 mb-4 max-md:mb-0 max-md:px-2 shrink-0" aria-label="POINT 04"><span class="md:hidden">04</span><span class="hidden md:inline" aria-hidden="true">POINT 04</span></span>
            <h3 class="advantage-point__title font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink leading-snug mb-5 max-md:mb-0 max-md:flex-1 max-md:min-w-0">資産価値を上げる提案ができる</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">単にきれいにするリフォームではなく、売れる・貸せる・高く評価されるリフォームを考えます。<br class="hidden md:block">水回りの刷新・間取りの変更・断熱改善など、不動産価値を上げる改修を提案します。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-12 md:mt-14 flex justify-center" data-reveal>
      <a href="/concept" class="site-btn site-btn--md site-btn--outline-ink">
        <span class="site-btn__inner">選ばれる理由を詳しく見る<svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg></span>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

